     2	
     3	Reference for the next 9 process area sections. Derived from Chris Trumble's review of the CRM sample, May 4, 2026. Apply consistently across all sections. Update this file when new conventions surface.
     4	
     5	---
     6	
     7	## Verified people and entities
     8	
     9	Use these names exactly. Do not abbreviate, paraphrase, or reorder.
    10	
    11	| Role | Name | Notes |
    12	|---|---|---|
    13	| KBM (the company) | **KBM Hogue** | Not "Hoag." Full company name when first introduced; "KBM" thereafter is acceptable |
    14	| Pivot (the company) | **Pivot Interiors** | Full name when first introduced; "Pivot" thereafter is acceptable |
