_Unification/working/pivot-brds-md/Project_Management.md:896:This section documents the SuiteApps, third\-party integrations, and external system connections required to support the Project Management/Workfront process area\. These components extend core NetSuite Orion functionality to meet Pivot Interiors' specific operational requirements\.
_Unification/working/pivot-brds-md/Project_Management.md:992:Current Workfront request volumes \(5,300 labor quotes, 3,200 work orders, 10,596 orders, 7,324 proposals over 18 months\) represent typical operational load and will not significantly increase at go\-live\.
