_Unification/working/pivot-brds-md/Project_Management.md:1074:Key stakeholders \(Brian Hagerty, Amanda Beaudin, Sandra Rudloff, Marie Guerrero, Sherri Nuzum\) will remain available for discovery validation, UAT, and training activities\.
_Unification/working/pivot-brds-md/Project_Management.md:1186:Finance / Sandra Rudloff
