Operations/KBMH/3 Output/BRD_Operations_v1.0.md:1423:The Field Service app must work without internet connectivity because many installation sites have poor or no cell service. PMs need to download work order information in the morning, work offline throughout the day (creating punch items, taking photos, documenting work), and then sync when back online. This requires offline-capable database and sync engine.
Operations/KBMH/3 Output/BRD_Operations_v1.0.md:1427:Currently, PlanGrid allows PMs to generate and email status reports directly from the iPad. The team initially hadn't planned to replicate this in NetSuite Field Service app, but Wendy needs this capability. Marcus agreed to add this functionality: PMs can generate status reports (showing daily progress, punch items, photos, etc.) directly from the tablet and email them to clients without returning to the office.
