Operations/KBMH/3 Output/BRD_Operations_v1.0.md:1516:Punch items link directly to work order events. PM is assigned to a work order event, checks in, performs work, creates punch items. The punch items are directly associated with that work order, creating complete traceability of what was done and what issues remain.
